aVWell, the reason is, is because, when we're buying gas,
p125
aVwe're very invested in this sort of cognitive dissonance.
p126
aVI mean, we're angry at the one hand and we want to be somewhere else.
p127
aVWe don't want to be buying oil;
p128
aVwe want to be doing something green.
p129
aVAnd we get kind of in on our own con.
