aVwhich is we don't talk about
p135
aVreducing the amount of oil that we use.
p136
aVWe talk about energy independence. We talk about hydrogen cars.
p137
aVWe talk about biofuels that haven't been invented yet.
p138
aVAnd so, cognitive dissonance
p139
aVis part and parcel of the way that we deal with oil,
p140
